  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <h1 class="display-4 fw-extrabold mb-3">Return & Refund <span class="text-primary">Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-5">Hassle-free 14-day returns with complimentary reverse shipping for our premium customers.</p>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-shield-check text-primary me-2"></i> 14-Day Return Guarantee</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
          At ToyBerry, we pride ourselves on curating only the highest-quality luxury toys. However, if your purchase does not bring absolute joy to your child, you may return the item within 14 days of delivery for a full refund or exchange.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-patch-exclamation text-primary me-2"></i> Conditions for Return</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">To be eligible for a refund, returned toys must meet the following criteria:</p>
        <ul class="text-muted lh-lg">
          <li>The product must be completely unused and in its original, undamaged condition.</li>
          <li>All components, manuals, accessories, stickers, and tags must be present inside the package.</li>
          <li>The toy must remain in its original box with seals intact (especially for collectibles, building blocks, and sealed electronic toys).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-arrow-repeat text-primary me-2"></i> Return Process</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">Initiating a return is simple and automated:</p>
        <ol class="text-muted lh-lg">
          <li>Send an email to <strong>returns@toyberry.in</strong> with your order number and reason for return, or drop a message via our contact form.</li>
          <li>Our delivery agents will contact you to organize a free reverse pickup from your home.</li>
          <li>Once our quality team inspects the returned product, your refund will be authorized.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3"><i class="bi bi-cash-stack text-primary me-2"></i> Refund Details</h3>
        <p class="text-muted lh-lg">
          Refunds are issued directly to the original payment source. For Credit Card/Stripe payments, it typically takes 5 to 7 business days for the funds to reflect in your account. For Cash On Delivery (COD) orders, our customer care team will request your bank account details for a direct, secure IMPS/NEFT bank transfer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

